name: Comfort me, comfort food
description: It's raining outside, it's raining inside your mind. All gloom and doom. In times like these, I usually turn to my comfort food, a bowl of instant noodle with a runny sunny side up, slices of bird eye chillies and fried shallots sprinkled over the whole bowl. Veggie is optional. Dip in that kerupuk (no it's not "cracker" in English), and let the whole combination hug you and give you the warmth you need.
